					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="5 Ways to Remarket You Can Start Using Now" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20150710163725-marketing-tools.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
